{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_李天狗",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·出山口·李天狗救场对白"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "哦豁……我的腰……我这是、我刚才咋子了……",
      "next": "n_ltg_scold"
    },
    "n_ltg_scold": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "李天狗"
      },
      "text": "大半夜在林子头鬼吼鬼叫——你嫌命长迈?",
      "next": "n_gjg_grope"
    },
    "n_gjg_grope": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "啊？喊咋子了……我脚杆还在不嘛……",
      "next": "n_ltg_rule"
    },
    "n_ltg_rule": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "李天狗"
      },
      "text": "走夜路，听到人喊你、万不能应。你刚才那通折腾——又吃了人家供的、又开口骂人家——它问一声、你回半个字，魂就归它管。",
      "next": "n_gjg_bluff"
    },
    "n_gjg_bluff": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "嗨呀——你看嘛我穿的啥子？这还要你教？小道我吃的就是这碗饭。",
      "next": "n_gjg_pack"
    },
    "n_gjg_pack": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "……嘿，没落没落。麻烦你了哈。",
      "next": "n_ltg_smell"
    },
    "n_ltg_smell": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "李天狗"
      },
      "text": "……你身上这股味。你，去过桃溪?",
      "next": "n_gjg_taoxibrag"
    },
    "n_gjg_taoxibrag": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "桃溪？哪个没去过嘛——几年前我还过去教训了一个女妖嘞！那地方我熟，熟得很!",
      "next": "n_flag_actions"
    },
    "n_flag_actions": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "grantRuleLayer",
          "params": {
            "ruleId": "rule_no_touch_offering",
            "layer": "li"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "setFlag",
          "params": {
            "key": "met_litiangou",
            "value": true
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "n_ltg_farewell"
    },
    "n_ltg_farewell": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "李天狗"
      },
      "text": "……鬼神可敬。命在你自己手上，莫叫人替你拿了去。——好自为之吧。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  },
  "preconditions": []
}
